when I need something.

04:54.163 --> 04:56.905
Because you're the only one
I can trust.

04:57.906 --> 04:59.560
Please, George?

04:59.603 --> 05:01.301
[dog barks in distance]

05:01.344 --> 05:03.607
Why don't you come through?

05:03.651 --> 05:04.913
[sighs]

05:04.956 --> 05:06.218
Beth?

05:09.309 --> 05:10.962
You know what? Fuck it.

05:11.006 --> 05:12.921
Find someone else to track down
your little friends.

05:12.964 --> 05:14.183
No, no, no. No, no.

05:14.226 --> 05:15.663
George, I-I want to come.

05:15.706 --> 05:18.405
I do. I just, I'm-I'm at work.

05:18.448 --> 05:19.623
And, um...

05:19.667 --> 05:21.799
the sooner I talk to Chevy,

05:21.843 --> 05:23.888
the sooner I can come over.

05:25.107 --> 05:26.717
Uh...

05:26.761 --> 05:29.416
you could... you could give me
a tour of your boat.

05:31.069 --> 05:33.158
For real?

05:33.202 --> 05:34.899
Yeah.

05:36.423 --> 05:39.251
Yeah, I've been thinking
about you.

05:39.295 --> 05:41.210
About that kiss.

05:41.253 --> 05:42.820
