05:42.864 --> 05:45.127
Oh, God, I'm sorry.
It's this gum that I chew.

05:45.170 --> 05:46.607
-I...
-No, no, no, it was...

05:46.650 --> 05:48.173
it was nice, it was...

05:48.217 --> 05:49.697
it was like a...

05:49.740 --> 05:51.742
summer garden.

05:53.004 --> 05:56.921
Yeah, well,
you-you tasted like hot dogs.

05:56.965 --> 05:59.271
[laughs]:
Yeah, fuck you.

05:59.315 --> 06:02.144
-[laughs]
-Hey, so, uh,
after you see Chevy,

06:02.187 --> 06:03.885
you'll... you'll come over?

06:03.928 --> 06:05.452
Uh, yeah. Yeah, I will.

06:05.495 --> 06:07.541
All right. Check your texts.

06:08.846 --> 06:10.239
[phone dings]

06:11.675 --> 06:13.373
[whispers]:
Yes. Go.

06:14.504 --> 06:16.550
[dog barking in distance]

06:28.300 --> 06:29.998
[door buzzes]

06:31.216 --> 06:32.435
Hey, baby.

06:32.479 --> 06:34.437
-Hey, baby!
-[laughing]

06:34.481 --> 06:37.440
-How you been?
-I'm okay.

06:37.484 --> 06:39.616
You know.
[chuckles]

06:39.660 --> 06:41.792
You're so lucky you're
on the inside, I'm telling you.

06:41.836 --> 06:44.578
The world has lost
its damn mind.

06:44.621 --> 06:45.840
But...

06:45.883 --> 06:47.581
I'm getting prepped.

06:47.624 --> 06:50.148
-You know I am.
-Mm-hmm.

06:50.192 --> 06:51.715
[quietly]:
Did a big run last night.

06:51.759 --> 06:54.109
Got kerosene,
a couple of bolt-action rifles,

06:54.152 --> 06:56.503
Sex in the Cityon DVD.

06:56.546 --> 06:58.461
-That's cool.
-[laughs]: Yeah.

06:58.505 --> 06:59.854
The van is finally...

06:59.897 --> 07:01.769
[clicking tongue]
...fully loaded.

07:01.812 --> 07:03.292
[Patty laughs]

07:03.335 --> 07:05.294
Been dreaming about ya.

07:05.337 --> 07:08.340
-Uh-huh.
-The two of us on the open road,

07:08.384 --> 07:10.386
-Yeah.
-living how we damn please.

07:10.430 --> 07:11.822
GUARD [in distance]:
Open the gate!

07:11.866 --> 07:13.084
[door buzzes]

07:13.128 --> 07:14.956
What's wrong?

07:16.740 --> 07:19.395
Hey. Talk to me.

07:19.439 --> 07:21.876
Nah, i-it's nothing. I'm fine.
[clears throat]

07:21.919 --> 07:23.486
Huh.

07:23.530 --> 07:25.836
Well, you've been talking
to someone.

07:25.880 --> 07:28.099
Like, for hours.

07:28.143 --> 07:29.840
What, you didn't think
I'd notice?

07:33.496 --> 07:35.455
Bills come to me, you know.

07:35.498 --> 07:36.804
So who is it?

07:36.847 --> 07:38.501
Who's this...

07:38.545 --> 07:40.416
0-1-8-3 number?

07:40.460 --> 07:41.896
Baby, why-why are you worrying
about things

07:41.939 --> 07:43.245
you don't need to worry about?

07:43.288 --> 07:44.942
It's-it's no one.

07:45.943 --> 07:47.379
Have it your way.

07:47.423 --> 07:48.946
I'll just have to track
the bitch down.

07:48.990 --> 07:50.470
Oh, Patty, baby, listen,
it's nothing.

07:50.513 --> 07:53.168
It's just, she's a...
she's a journalist.

07:53.211 --> 07:56.693
-A journalist?
-Yeah, she's gonna help me
get out.

07:56.737 --> 07:59.609
[Patty laughs]

07:59.653 --> 08:02.090
What's her big plan, huh?

08:02.133 --> 08:04.658
She gonna dig you a tunnel? Hmm?

08:04.701 --> 08:06.703
Ship you in a box?

08:06.747 --> 08:08.879
Christ almighty,
you are so goddamn naiïve.

08:08.923 --> 08:10.968
No, l-look,
if she gets me out of here,

08:11.012 --> 08:12.187
then we can be together.

08:12.230 --> 08:13.536
I'm-I'm doing this for us.

08:13.580 --> 08:15.233
Listen to me.

08:15.277 --> 08:17.584
Whatever it is she's promising,
she can't deliver, okay?

08:17.627 --> 08:19.716
It's not real.
[scoffs]

08:19.760 --> 08:23.241
There's no such thing
as journalism anymore.

08:23.285 --> 08:25.330
They're all scammers
and con artists.

08:25.374 --> 08:26.767
But this?

08:26.810 --> 08:29.944
You and me? This is real.

08:29.987 --> 08:31.859
This is something
you could count on.

08:31.902 --> 08:33.556
And you should be thanking
your lucky stars,

08:33.600 --> 08:36.603
but instead you're what,
trading up? Huh?

08:36.646 --> 08:39.344
For some fake-news bitch
keeping your head in the clouds?

08:39.388 --> 08:40.563
Can I fuckin' help you?!

08:40.607 --> 08:41.869
S-Sorry.

08:41.912 --> 08:43.871
Well, I am tired
of giving so much

08:43.914 --> 08:45.786
and not getting in return, okay?

08:45.829 --> 08:47.875
Don't think I'll be leaving
any commissary today.

08:47.918 --> 08:49.485
No, quit freaking!

08:49.529 --> 08:51.095
I haven't talked to her
in a week-- it's over.

08:51.139 --> 08:52.532
Check-check your bills.

08:53.794 --> 08:55.273
J...

08:55.317 --> 08:56.797
[exhales]

08:57.798 --> 08:58.929
Patty-cake...

08:58.973 --> 09:00.409
Mm-mm.

09:00.452 --> 09:02.498
-Baby love...
-No.

09:03.673 --> 09:06.894
Vanilla scoop?

09:06.937 --> 09:08.156
Hmm?

09:09.157 --> 09:11.986
♪ Caramel swirl.♪

09:13.553 --> 09:15.903
You know you're
my number one, right?

09:17.905 --> 09:19.776
Stop playin'. Come here.

09:21.778 --> 09:24.259
[whispers]:
I don't like feeling like this.

09:24.302 --> 09:26.609
Well, then don't feel like this.

09:27.654 --> 09:29.525
You'll ditch her? For me?

09:29.569 --> 09:31.745
It's already done.

09:32.746 --> 09:34.704
-[softly]: Okay.
-Yeah?

09:34.748 --> 09:36.053
I got to go.

09:36.097 --> 09:38.621
-I got to go.
-Uh...

09:38.665 --> 09:41.493
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.

09:53.636 --> 09:55.595
GUARD:
Open the gate!

10:03.472 --> 10:04.995
