Uh, are you Chevy?

10:37.767 --> 10:39.639
Who are you?

10:39.682 --> 10:41.292
Oh. I'm Beth.

10:41.336 --> 10:42.816
Hi. Sorry.

10:42.859 --> 10:46.210
