ALLEGRA:
Yeah, you know, I couldn't go
to the trial, either.

11:38.785 --> 11:40.395
I had too much going on, child.

11:40.438 --> 11:43.311
No, my whole life was
a mess, honey.

11:43.354 --> 11:45.879
What about you, Chevy?

11:46.880 --> 11:48.751
Chevonne.

11:48.795 --> 11:50.492
Ch-Chevonne, uh...

11:50.535 --> 11:51.841
do you visit her?

11:51.885 --> 11:53.887
Were you two close?

11:55.540 --> 11:58.239
-Girl, you need a drink?
-Mm-hmm.

11:58.282 --> 12:00.676
-But go easy on the vodka
this time.
-[quiet]: Don't worry about it.

12:00.720 --> 12:02.112
[laughter]

12:02.156 --> 12:04.680
[hip-hop continues playing]

12:04.724 --> 12:07.727
-Yeah, they were close,
all right.
-Mm.

12:07.770 --> 12:10.338
-Like sisters.
-Mm-hmm. Best friends.

12:10.381 --> 12:11.905
