12:27.355 --> 12:29.705
-I mean, anything?
-Oh.

12:29.749 --> 12:32.664
-[mocking]: Please? Anything?
-[laughing] Anything.

12:32.708 --> 12:36.799
-What? What?
-No, you just sounded so sad
right there.

12:38.105 --> 12:40.672
Look, all I know is,

12:40.716 --> 12:44.111
