somewhere else to be. Right?

13:12.226 --> 13:15.795
-Actually,
I'd love to get my nails done.
-Perfect.

13:15.838 --> 13:18.232
BETH:
But maybe if you have something
a little less permanent?

13:18.275 --> 13:19.581
-Oh, yeah, I've got you.
-Yeah?

13:19.624 --> 13:21.061
Yeah.

13:22.889 --> 13:25.282
[sighs]:
Okay.

13:25.326 --> 13:27.154
ALLEGRA:
So, uh,

13:27.197 --> 13:29.243
you-you think Toni's innocent?

13:29.286 --> 13:30.722
Um, yeah, of course.

13:30.766 --> 13:32.159
What about you?

13:32.202 --> 13:33.813
Nah, I don't think she did it.

13:33.856 --> 13:35.640
